---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-sm text-[#2b361c]">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#636b3f] mb-4">Collaborators</h1>

        <p class="mb-4">
            The AURA Protocol is an open and collaborative effort driven by experts in artificial intelligence, scientific reproducibility, and digital ethics. It brings together researchers, developers, and educators committed to promoting transparency and accountability in the use of generative AI.
        </p>

        <!-- Lead Contributor -->
        <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#b17036] mb-2">Lead Contributor:</h2>
            <p>
                <strong>Dr. Fausto David Cortes Rojas</strong> – Researcher and professor in Biomedical Engineering, with specialization in AI transparency, image processing, and ethical applications of generative models. He has authored peer-reviewed publications and led interdisciplinary research projects at the intersection of technology and medicine.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-xs text-[#636b3f] mt-2 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc list-inside">
                <li>
                    <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5224-5710" class="hover:text-aura-leather" target="_blank">ORCID Profile</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://www.webofscience.com/wos/author/record/MFI-2232-2025" class="hover:text-aura-leather" target="_blank">Web of Science Author Record</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Contributing Technologies -->
        <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#b17036] mb-2">Contributing Technologies:</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>OpenAI API – GPT-based generation used during protocol drafting</li>
                <li>Astro Framework – Static site generation and publishing</li>
                <li>GitHub – Collaborative version control and public contributions</li>
                <li>Vercel – Deployment and hosting of the official AURA site</li>
                <li>AWS (Amazon Web Services) – Backend integrations and cloud storage</li>
                <li>Tailwind CSS – Modern and responsive interface styling</li>
                <li>Node.js – Server-side JavaScript runtime for development and deployment</li>
                <li>React – Interactive components within the Astro framework</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Invitation to Collaborate -->
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-[#d4a369] italic">
            Interested in contributing to the protocol, suggesting improvements, or joining the initiative? Reach out via
            <a href="mailto:fdavid.cortezr@cinvestav.mx" class="hover:text-aura-leather"> email</a>
            or submit proposals on
            <a href="https://github.com/drfcortes/aura.org" class="hover:text-aura-leather"> GitHub</a>.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
